    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently runs roughly and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping, suggesting it may need a major overhaul or replacement soon. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several large dents, significant rust patches on the rocker panels, and clear coat failure across most surfaces. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. This is being sold as-is, ideally for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts.",
