    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking value and utility. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a solid car at a very accessible price point!",
